1. *Dragi* moji, doviđenja! (Dear ones, goodbye!)
2. Da li će i moj *dragi* biti tu? (Will my dear one be there too?)
3. *Dragom* srcu, dobro je! (A dear heart is well!)
4. Želim da mi *dragi* budeš uz mene. (I want you to be with me, my dear.)
5. *Dragim* prijateljima, hvala vam! (Thank you, dear friends!)